msg: Because the ClearParser dependency parser and SRL wrappers are built using ClearTK, we can automatically generate the descriptor files using WriteClearParserDescriptors.java.  The existing version had a path relative to the Annotator Java source for the TypeSystem descriptor instead of relative to the desc/analysis_engine target directory.
WriteClearParserDescriptors.java has been updated and the corresponding descriptors have been regenerated.
